# RiteMark Patch: Default Ritemark Light Theme
#
# Purpose: Default to Ritemark Light theme on all platforms at every level
#
# Why: VS Code defaults to Dark theme on desktop. Ritemark targets non-technical
#      users who expect a Light theme. This patch changes defaults at 3 levels:
#      1. Bootstrap (main process + renderer splash) - first render colors
#      2. Workbench theme service - placeholder theme type before extensions load
#      3. Configuration defaults - colorTheme setting defaults to 'Ritemark Light'
#
# File(s): src/vs/code/electron-sandbox/workbench/workbench.js
#          src/vs/platform/theme/electron-main/themeMainService.ts
#          src/vs/workbench/services/themes/browser/workbenchThemeService.ts
#          src/vs/workbench/services/themes/common/themeConfiguration.ts
# Created: 2025-02-07
# Updated: 2026-02-16
#
